text: Les Velluire-sur-Vendée is a commune. It is found in the region Pays de la Loire in the Vendée department in the west of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2019 and consists of the former communes of Le Poiré-sur- Velluire (the seat) and Velluire.Arrêté préfectoral 17 August 2018 == References == Category:2019 establishments in France Category:Communes in Vendée
title: Les Velluire-sur-Vendée
